[? if tolerating_parties_display != "None" : Tolerated by: [+ tolerating_parties_display +] ?]

Government coalition votes: [+ government_total_votes +][? if tolerating_parties_display != "None" :  ([+ government_effective_pct +] effective with toleration) ?]

